---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
import ImageText from '../../components/ImageText.astro';
import BookingCTA from '../../components/BookingCTA.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Post-Surgical Patients"
	description="Structured, progressive rehabilitation after ACL, joint replacement, rotator cuff, spinal and foot and ankle surgery."
>
	<PageHero
		title="Post-Surgical Patients"
		breadcrumb="Post-Surgical Patients"
	/>

	<ImageText
		image="/who-we-help/gym-consultation.jpg"
		imageAlt="Physiotherapist talking with a client in the gym"
	>
		<p>Surgery is often the beginning of the recovery journey, not the end of it. The quality of rehabilitation in the weeks and months following an operation directly determines your outcome, and at Balance we provide post-surgical rehabilitation that is structured, progressive and tailored to your specific procedure, your body and your goals.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<ImageText
		reverse
		altBg
		image="/who-we-help/resistance-bands.jpg"
		imageAlt="Colourful resistance bands hanging from an outdoor training bar"
	>
		<p>We work across the full range of post-surgical presentations, including ACL reconstructions, hip and knee replacements, rotator cuff repairs, spinal procedures, and foot and ankle surgeries, with the depth and breadth of expertise that complex cases require. With 25 specialists under one roof, nothing falls through the gaps.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<ImageText
		image="/who-we-help/soccer-player-red.jpg"
		imageAlt="Footballer in a red kit running with the ball"
	>
		<p>Hydrotherapy reduces load through healing structures while enabling movement and strength work that would be impossible on land at the same stage of recovery. Our anti-gravity treadmill allows safe, progressive loading of healing tissue earlier than conventional rehabilitation permits, often accelerating timelines significantly.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<ImageText
		reverse
		altBg
		image="/who-we-help/skier-tricks.jpg"
		imageAlt="Skier performing tricks in fresh mountain snow"
	>
		<p>Beyond your formal appointments, our studios, gym and movement spaces are available daily, free of charge. We give you clear milestones, honest timelines and the knowledge to understand your recovery, because informed patients recover better.</p>
		<p>Returning to full function takes time, commitment and expert guidance. At Balance, we provide all three.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<BookingCTA />
</Layout>
